# -*- mode:org -*-
#+TITLE: NuSMV notes

a repo to play around with [[nusmv.fbk.eu][NuSMV]].

* useful shell commands

- =go= :: initialize system

- =pick_state [-i] [-r]= :: pick initial state

- =simulate= :: [-i] for interactively choosing transitions
                [-k] limits number of steps

* async processess
are apparently being deprecated, so should probably be avoided?
